text: Mayar Hany, also known as Mayar Hany Abdelrahman and Mayar Hany Mohamed (born 5 February 1997 in Cairo) is an Egyptian professional squash player. As of February 2018, she was ranked number 34 in the world. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian female squash players Category:Sportspeople from Cairo
